  "description": "When handling Silicon Nitride in high-heat settings like aerospace parts, focus on its excellent thermal stability, which holds the material firm and undamaged amid extreme temperatures. Unlike common ceramics that crack under rapid heating or cooling, this makes it ideal for tough components in engines or cutting tools. Keep an eye during processing for any surface deposits that could disrupt uniform heating, and tweak your methods to deliver smooth, dependable results.",
